2. Paka ya Lekgetho ya 2017
2.1. Kabinete e leboga baduelalekgetho botlhe bao ba setseng ba dirile dipusetso tsa lekgetho tsa ngwaga wa lekgetho wa 2016/17.
2.2. Madikokoanyo ao a kokoangwang go tswa mo lekgethong la megolo a kgontsha puso go nna le bokgoni jwa go tlamela ka ditirelo tse di tlhokagalang thata mmogo le go tshegetsa maAforika Borwa a a dikobo dikhutshwane.
