Nkhensani Nkosi o ne a batla go fetola se.
O ne a rata go dira diaparo, mme gape o ne a batla go dira diaparo tse di neng di bontsha ditšo tsa selegae le gore batho ba nne motlotlo go nna Maaforika.
Ka ngwaga wa 2000, o ne a simolola Stoned Cherrie, mofuta wa diaparo o o dirang diaparo tsa Aforika, ditshwantsho le dikgatiso tse di tumileng.
Mmegadikgang Ferial Haffajee o ne a lebagane le bothata jo fa a bua maikutlo a gagwe.
Ferial o tlholegetse kwa Motsekapa, fela mme wa gagwe o ne a batla gore e nne mmueledi.
O ithutetse molao, mme o ne a sa o rate, jaanong e rile a fetsa dithuto tsa gagwe, a simolola go dira jaaka moithuti wa bobegadikgang kwa lekwalodikgang la Mail & Guardian ka 1991.
Ferial o ne a kwala maikaelelo a gagwe mo botshelong mme nngwe ya ona e ne e le go nna mookamedi wa lekwalodikgang.
Morago ga a sena go direla makwalodikgang a a farologaneng, o ne a nna mookamedi wa Mail & Guardian ka Ferikgong 2004, se sa mo dira mookamedi wa ntlha wa mosadi wa lekwalodikgang le le botlhokwa mo Aforika Borwa.
Morago, o ne a nna mookamedi wa City Press.
Kwa pontshong ya diaparo ya boditšhaba kwa New York ka 2009, dimotlelara tse di apereng diaparo tsa Stoned Cherrie ba ne ba tsamaya mo seraleng ka mekgabo e e mebalabala, dibaga le mekgabiso.
Diaparo tsa ga Nkhensani di ne di dirisitse matsela a mefutafuta.
Dikete le mesese di ne di na le ditaele tse di farologaneng, le dikipara tsa gagwe, tse di gatisitsweng sefatlhego sa ga Steve Biko, e ne ya nna letshwao la diaparo tsa gagwe.
Ka moaparo, o bontshitse khumo ya mefutafuta ya ngwao ya Aforika Ferial o na le maikutlo a a maatla mo dilong tse dintsi, le go anela dikgang tsa Aforika Borwa jaaka a di bona – le fa batho ba sa dumelane le ena.
Ferial ka gale o ne a fetola ka go ikarabela ka go tlhalosa boemo ka moo a bonang dilo ka teng mme a bua ka go ipela a re: “Ke se ke leng sona.” Buka ya gagwe, dipuisano le dipotsolotso tse a nnileng le tsona jaaka mmegadikgang mo dingwageng tse dintsi.
Jaaka mookamedi, o dumela gore o tshwanetse go nna mmegadikgang yo o tlhwatlhwa, o kgone go tsaya ditshwetso le go nna le boitlhamedi.
Maikaelelo a gagwe a akaretsa go anela dikgang tsa tshotlako kgatlhanong le basadi, go itumelela basadi ba ba nang le bokgoni le go emela “boeteledipele jwa popego e e farologaneng”.
Nkhensani e ne e le ena wa pele go dirisa matsela a Aforika mo mekgabisong ya segompieno go bontsha ditaele tsa Aforika dirang diaparo tsa maemo, ditlhako, dikgabisi, dibenyane le dihutse tse di mo dinakong le Seaforika ditsela.
Gompieno fa o lebelela dimakasine tsa moaparo, ga o na fela go bona ditiro tsa bona, o tla bona le dimotlelara tsa Bantsho ka bontsi.
Stoned Cherrie e re rutile go apara diaparo tsa Seaforika ka boipelo.
Ke rata ntlha ya gore go tshwaiwa diphoso ga go a ka ga emisa Ferial go lwela go utlwiwa le go nna moeteledipele mo tirong ya gagwe.
