Nal’ibali news Dikgang tsa Nal’ibali Nal’ibali celebration Ngwaga mongwe le mongwe ka Letsatsi la Lefatshe la Puisetsogodimo, Nal’ibali e gakolola mongwe le mongwe mo Aforika Borwa ka ga mesola ya go buisetsa bana kwa godimo.
Go tloga ka 2013, o re thusitse go atisa lorato lwa mainane le go buisa go bana ba le bantsintsi.
Sentlentle, go ya ka LitWorld (barulaganyi ba boditšhabatšhaba ba Letsatsi la Lefatshe la Puisetsogodimo), moletlo wa Nal’ibali ke mongwe wa meletlo Ka lekgetlho lwa ntlha lwa Letsatsi la Lefatshe la Puisetsogodimo ka 2013, o re thusitse go buisetsa bana ba le 13 401.
Monongwaga ka 5 Tlhakole 2020, re fitlheletse bana ba le 2 925 224 mo nageng ka bophara!
Ke rekoto e ntšhwa ya Nal’ibali le Aforika Borwa!
Mo dipaakanyong tsa Letsatsi la Lefatshe la Puisetsogodimo Nal’ibali e tlhamile leinane le le kgethegileng.
Monongwaga leinane la rona le bidiwa, Letsatsi le re le gopolang, le kwadilwe ke mokwadi wa fa gae yo o itsegeng thata e bile ke moitseanape wa thuto ya go buisa le go kwala, Lorato Trok mme ditshwantsho di thadilwe ke Rico.
Badiragatsi ba yona ke dikgantshwane tse di rategang tsa Nal’ibali, Lorato o kwadile leinane ka Setswana, puo ya gagwe ya gae, mme le fetoletswe mo dipuong tsotlhe tsa semmuso.
